document_data.Abilities:
The [[tattoo]]s on his body granted him different kinds of enchantments, such as:
* Sending warmth flowing through his body, which was particularly useful when flying on his griffon;
* Cooling his body when needed;
* Bestowing upon him an enchantment of accuracy; and
* Alleviating magically provoked weakness.

He had [[spell]]s to sober himself at will. He could conjure [[dart]]s of blue light from his fingertips that veered to strike even a dodging victim and seldom missed their intended target. Aoth could also conjure a crackling, forking flare of lightning.
